      description "Distribution of hardware resource utilization level for each Capacity Module. Hardware resource utilization level corresponds to 100 * (Total number of connected UEs + Total number of configured SCells) / Maximum RRC Connected Users. Maximum number of RRC connected users is limited by Baseband hardware capacity. For more information, see Supported Capacity and Configurations. PDF ranges: [0]: [0..5]% [1]: ]5..10]% [2]: ]10..15]% [3]: ]15..20]% [4]: ]20..25]% [5]: ]25..30]% [6]: ]30..35]% [7]: ]35..40]% [8]: ]40..45]% [9]: ]45..50]% [10]: ]50..55]% [11]: ]55..60]% [12]: ]60..65]% [13]: ]65..70]% [14]: ]70..75]% [15]: ]75..80]% [16]: ]80..85]% [17]: ]85..90]% [18]: ]90..95]% [19]: ]95..100]% Scanner: Not included in any predefined scanner.";
